I found the exact blocker: the inherited `encoder.weight` and `encoder.bias` from `LowRankResidualSparseCoder` were never used in `lowrank_multi_branch_residual`, and those are exactly the DDP-unused parameters. I’m patching the family so the inherited residual encoder becomes an always-on anchor branch, which preserves the original experiment while closing the reduction bug.
